description: Traditional Dominican food with a modern twist. Favorites include our famous dominican burger "Chimi"  (aka The Best Chimi) and our deep fried chicken, pork and beef. Distinctive, delectable, mouth watering food for a very reasonable price! Tostones (Fried Plantain), Empanads de Yuca and Yaroa are other classic favorites of ours that we serve. Beverages include  Merengue Soda and Cocoa Cola canned drinks and bottled water.
name: Pa'La Fristura y Aigo Mas
